column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.nvote, zns.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_smooth_weighted_fraction as elliptical, zns.t0#_spiral_a0#_spiral_weighted_fraction as spiral, zns.t0#_bar_a0#_bar_weighted_fraction as bar FROM Galaxy as p JOIN zoo2MainSpecz AS zns ON p.objid = zns.dr7objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
